{"tid":1169282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我無力解決脫歐問題」　文翠珊宣佈7/6辭任黨魁","createTime":"2019-05-24T09:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T17:10:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85d8195edb43e104a34b24c19fa2adab381c2325","tid":1169282,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"英國首相文翠珊發表聲明，宣佈7/6辭任黨魁。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊面對極大下台壓力，她周五與黨內後座議員的「1922委員會」主席布雷迪（Sir Graham Brady）會面，討論離任確實時間表後，公開辭職。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊下台後，除了她之外保守黨任何議員均可競逐黨魁，之後由議員舉行連串投票，淘汰最低票數的參選人，直至選出兩位候選人為止，預計整個過程歷時幾星期。之後保守黨全體黨員估計會在7月投票選出新黨魁，目前的大熱人選包括前外相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）、前脫歐事務大臣藍韜文（Dominic Raab）及外相侯俊偉（Jeremy Hunt）。<br />\n<br />\n黨魁選舉刻不容緩，因為英國脫歐延至10月31日，保守黨希望在9月底年會前選出新黨魁並發表講話，以團結保守黨。"},{"pid":"a351bd100ffcd8087207ab1d25c754fb59d3f0b3","tid":1169282,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190524/59635274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190524%2F59635274&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=5ea9bc7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190524%2F59635274&h=a1a96058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190524/59635274</a>"},{"pid":"26491ef8b366bb1f3d5225ecf21265c296148e35","tid":1169282,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"到底邊個個接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fe7d110c62829ea08c22b7e2a0bf8d3f69bbc8","tid":1169282,"uid":53577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"jeremy hunt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那雞諜老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85a744d93767ab31ccfaa1807a43e49ba0bf1d0","tid":1169282,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:37:35.000Z","msg":"重新大選啦。 保守黨個個都犯眾憎"},{"pid":"f3ba12656024cbdd9e41f342c1bd7d5ba211ec4d","tid":1169282,"uid":34336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c1ab3298ef8af6bad80422b3b0e82ab2ec44ebb","tid":1169282,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"叫約翰遜條撚樣上去做就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條死肥佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faaf611dc09b2cad1a6f4615f29bec3e8961613","tid":1169282,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　我</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">覺得</span><span style=\"color: green;\">文翠珊</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">好似</span>被人玩，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１６年</span><span style=\"color: green;\">英國</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">公投</span>爆冷脫歐，<span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">原先</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">留歐，</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">是不是</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">應該</span><span style=\"color: red;\">選</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一個</span><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span>脫歐<span style=\"color: violet;\">做</span><span style=\"color: green;\">首相？她</span><span style=\"color: red;\">被選了</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">做</span><span style=\"color: green;\">首相，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">好似</span>被擺上枱，<span style=\"color: brown;\">經常</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">睇</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">新聞</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">見到</span><span style=\"color: green;\">她</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">係</span><span style=\"color: green;\">國會</span><span style=\"color: red;\">硬銷</span>脫歐<span style=\"color: brown;\">好似</span>小丑、儍婆，<span style=\"color: brown;\">但</span><span style=\"color: green;\">國會議員</span>又唔聽佢講，唔做好過做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　我本身</span>孤陋寡聞不知道<span style=\"color: purple;\">留歐</span><span style=\"color: red;\">好，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">還是</span>脫歐<span style=\"color: red;\">好？</span></span></strong>"}]}